OL,3,CMinister says 'unacceptable' to
OL,4,Coverrule Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FWatch the full interview with Darren
OL,7,FJones on Good Morning Britain
OL,9,FIt is "beyond comprehension" that the
OL,10,FForeign Office had the "unacceptable"
OL,11,Fpower to override the security vetting
OL,12,Fprocess to clear Lord Peter Mandelson
OL,13,Fto become UK ambassador to the US, the
OL,14,Fchief secretary to the prime minister
OL,15,Fhas said.
OL,17,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain,
OL,18,FDarren Jones said he had suspended the
OL,19,FForeign Office and any other
OL,20,Forganisation's ability to overrule the
OL,21,Fadvice of the UK's vetting body.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776453069
OL,3,CMinister says 'unacceptable' to
OL,4,Coverrule Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FThe revelation that Mandelson had been
OL,7,Fappointed to the role despite failing
OL,8,Fthe process has brought the crisis
OL,9,Fback to the centre of government and
OL,10,Fhas led to renewed calls for the prime
OL,11,Fminister to resign.
OL,13,FJones told GMB he did not believe Keir
OL,14,FStarmer had misled Parliament over the
OL,15,Fissue while making statements about
OL,16,Fthe affair, which would be a breach of
OL,17,Fthe ministerial code.
OL,19,FJones said Starmer was "furious" at
OL,20,Fthe situation and would be updating
OL,21,FParliament about it on Monday.
OL,26,@{D@XOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
