OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776453069
OL,3,CMinister says 'unacceptable' to
OL,4,Coverrule Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office's top civil
OL,7,Fservant, Sir Olly Robbins, was
OL,8,Feffectively sacked after the
OL,9,Frevelation that officials took the
OL,10,Frare step of overruling the
OL,11,Frecommendation from UK Security
OL,12,FVetting.
OL,14,FThe prime minister was not aware that
OL,15,Fthe former Labour grandee was granted
OL,16,Fdeveloped vetting against the advice
OL,17,Fof UK Security Vetting until earlier
OL,18,Fthis week, the Government has said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
