PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776453069
OL,3,CMinister says 'unacceptable' to
OL,4,Coverrule Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FSpeaking to the BBC, Jones said Sir
OL,7,FKeir has not considered resigning over
OL,8,Fthe allegation he misled Parliament.
OL,10,FHe told BBC Breakfast: "The prime
OL,11,Fminister was right when he told the
OL,12,FHouse that due process had been
OL,13,Ffollowed, because it had, but the fact
OL,14,Fthat that process did not require
OL,15,Fofficials to tell the Foreign
OL,16,FSecretary or the Prime Minster that
OL,17,Fthey ignored the advice of security
OL,18,Fand vetting officials is totally
OL,19,Funacceptable."
OL,26,@rD@XOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
