OL,3,CMinister says 'unacceptable' to
OL,4,Coverrule Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FThat warning stemmed from the first
OL,7,Fpart of the checks, carried out by the
OL,8,FCabinet Office, which was based on
OL,9,Finformation in the public domain at
OL,10,Fthe time.
OL,12,FThe second was the highly confidential
OL,13,Fbackground vetting by security
OL,14,Fofficials, which followed the
OL,15,Fannouncement but came before Lord
OL,16,FMandelson took up his role in February
OL,17,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
